Zc","target":"recym9Dfibw7KdshX","label":"event"},{"source":"recrx0bO7aofdkeZc","target":"rec3IGuoFfX4wwc0u","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec7gYOReFEgakc2X","ref":"Matt.26.1","text":"And it came to pass, when Jesus had finished all these sayings, he said unto his disciples,","year":33},{"id":"recZHB1MRI9Vbjmkt","ref":"Matt.26.2","text":"Ye know that after two days is the feast of the passover, and the Son of man is betrayed to be crucified.","year":33},{"id":"recqzpfKNwdhty38V","ref":"Matt.26.3","text":"Then assembled together the chief priests, and the scribes, and the elders of the people, unto the palace of the high priest, who was called Caiaphas,","year":33},{"id":"recTNHPodBGqDnm7n","ref":"Matt.26.4","text":"And consulted that they might take Jesus by subtilty, and kill him.","year":33},{"id":"recIGRx77vC2YHz4q","ref":"Matt.26.5","text":"But they said, Not on the feast day, lest there be an uproar among the people.","year":33},{"id":"recVJKGRP7axvNzUJ","ref":"Matt.26.6","text":"Now when Jesus was in Bethany, in the house of Simon the leper,","year":33},{"id":"recMNYKorpkfjSWRl","ref":"Matt.26.7","text":"There came unto him a woman having an alabaster box of very precious ointment, and poured it on his head, as he sat at meat.","year":33},{"id":"recafJS98o5GM1IHJ","ref":"Matt.26.8","text":"But when his disciples saw it, they had indignation, saying, To what purpose is this waste?","year":33}]}
